            "text": " will be held at the 87-acre M1 Concourse facility just north of Detroit, and the 1.5-mile road course could provide similar high-speed entertainment as Goodwood's 1.1-mile hill climb event. Organizers for this event will be hosting a new Woodward Dream Show planned to kickoff this August in place of the cancelled ",
